00:21:29.800 --> 00:21:31.360
'Aku masuk ke dalam, Gungun.
Jangan kuatir.'

00:21:31.440 --> 00:21:32.880
Mohan, jangan masuk ke dalam.

00:21:35.920 --> 00:21:37.600
Mohan!  -Mohan!

00:21:41.480 --> 00:21:42.720
Gungun!